                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320906-27-defend381 t18320906-27-deflabel165"></join>. On the 21st of April, about six o'clock in the evening, I gave him three sovereigns to get change in the neighbourhood - he went out; I saw him no more till the 21st of July, when he was in custody.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18320906-27-person385">
                  BENJAMIN 
                  WEBB
